name: Grayskul
description: '''Grayskul''' is an American [[Hip hop music|hip hop]] duo based in [[Seattle, Washington]], consisting of rappers [[Onry Ozzborn]] and JFK Ninjaface. Since its formation in 2003, the group has released ten solo albums. The duo often collaborate with artists from the [[Hip hop music in the Pacific Northwest|Pacific Northwest hip hop]] collective [[Oldominion]].
